\id PHM - Southern Pastaza Quechua NT - Peru 2008 (DBL -2013) 
\h FILEMONRAYKU KILLKA 
\toc1 Filemonrayku Killka 
\toc2 Filemón 
\toc3 Flm 
\mt1 PABLOPA KILLKASHKAN KILLKA FILEMONRAYKU 
\c 1  
\s1 Pablo Timoteowa Filemonta saludanahun 
\p  
\v 1 Munashkanchi wawkinchi Filemón, ñuka Pablo wawki Timoteowa pakta kay kartata kanrayku killkahunchi. Ñuka Pablo Jesukristupa shiminta yachachik kashpaynimi kay karselpi churawashkakuna. Kan yuyashkanchi wawkinchi ñukanchishina Jesukristupa shiminta yachachikrayku kay kartata killkahunchi.  
\v 2 Chaymanta paninchi Apiarayku, ñukanchishina sinchita parisishpa yachachik wawkinchi Arkiporaykupas, tukuy wasikipi tantarik wawkikuna panikunaraykupas kay kartata killkahunchi.  
\v 3 Yayanchi Dios, Amunchi Jesukristupas kankunata llakichishpan yanapachun kushilla kawsanaykichipa. 
\s1 Pablo riman Filemonmanta kushikushkanta 
\p  
\v 4-5 Wawkini, ñuka Pablo yachashkani Amunchi Jesusta kirishpa, tukuy kirik masinchikunatapas alita yuyashpa kawsahushkaykita. Chayta yachashpaynimi tukuy uras mañahushpayni Yaya Diosta agradesini kanrayku.  
\v 6 Kan Jesusta kirihushkaykita shukkunata rimashpa kawsahunki. Chayraykumi Yaya Diosta mañani kanta yanapananpa ashwan alita ashwanta ashwanta asirtanaykipa pay ñukanchipi yapa alita rurashkanta Kristuta kushichishpa kawsananchipa.  
\v 7 Yapa kushilla kahuni, chaymantapas alita sinchikushkani kirikkunata yuyashpa kawsahushkaykita yachashpayni. Wawkini, paykunata alita sinchikuchishkaykirayku kushikushkani. 
\s1 Pablo Filemonta tapun Onesimota llakichinanpa 
\p  
\v 8 Alita rurak kashpayki shuk imata ruranaykipa tapunayani. Kristupa kamachishkan kashpayni atipaynima kanta kamachinata.  
\v 9-10 Chasna kamachinata atipashpaynipas mana kamachishkaykichu, yuyanakuhushkanchiraykumi kanta tapuni kasuwanaykipa. Ña ruku kashpayni chaymanta Kristu Jesuspa shiminta yachachishkaynirayku kay karselpi kahushpayni kanta tapuni Onesimorayku. Payka kay karselpi Jesukristumanta yachachishkaynita kirishkanraykumi kikin wawaynishina tukushka. 
\p  
\v 11 Kay rantishkayki runa Onesimoka ñawpa kanrayku mana alitachu kasushpa tarawak karka. Kunanka mana chasnanachu. Ñukata alitami yanapawahun, kanma kutishpan kantapas alitanami kasushpa yanapanka. 
\p  
\v 12 Kay wawkinita kunan kanma kachahuni. Yapa yuyashkayni wawkini kashpan ñukatashina alita yaykuchiy.  
\v 13 Jesukristu runakunata kishpichinanmanta yachachihushkaynirayku kay karselpi kahushpayni munaynima karka kay wawkini Onésimo ñukawa kiparishpan kanranti yanapawananpa.  
\v 14 Chasna munashpaynipas kan manara ari nishpaykika manami atipanichu payta kiparichinata. Manami munanichu kan mana munakta paywa yanapawanaykita. Ashwan ali kama, kan kikin munashpayki paywa yanapawanaykipa. 
\p  
\v 15 Onesimoka shuk punchakunatachari kanmanta anchuchirishka kashka, chaymanta wiñayparayku kanwa kawsananpana.  
\v 16 Mananami rantishkayki runashinallachu kanwa kawsanka, ashwan kunanka kamachinaykimanta ashwan tukurka. Yuyashka wawkinchimi tukushkana. Ñukaka payta yapami yuyani. Kanka ñukamanta ashwan pasata yuyanayki tiyan, kanta yanapak runayki kashkanrayku chaymantapas Jesukristuta kasuk masiki tukushkanrayku. 
\p  
\v 17 Imashnami ñukata kikin wawkikitashina yuyawanki, chasnallatata paytapas yuyashpayki wasikipi yaykuchiy.  
\v 18 Wawki Onésimo shuwashpa mitikushka kashpanka chasnallatata shuk imamanta kanta liwihushpanka ñukami pagashkayki.  
\v 19 Ñuka kayta kikin makiniwa killkahuni pagashkaykimi nishpa. Chasna rimashpaynipas ama kunkaychu kanta yachachishkaynirayku Jesukristuta katik tukushkaykita. Chasna kashpanmi kanka achkata liwiwahukshina kahunki.  
\v 20 Chayrayku wawkini, parihu Jesukristuta kirikkuna kashpanchi kay wawkinchita alita wasikipi yaykuchipay. Chasnashpayki shunkuynita kushichipay, imashnami ali kan rurananchipa Kristuwa shukllashina tukushkanchirayku. 
\p  
\v 21 Chasna killkani yachashpayni kasuwanaykita. Yachanimi tukuy munashkaynimanta pasata ruranaykitapas. 
\p  
\v 22 Chaymantapas shuk kwartuykita alichapay wasikipi paktanaynipa. Kirini Yaya Diosta mañahushkaykichirayku pay ñukata kuti kankunama paktachinanta. 
\s1 Wawkikuna saluduta kachanahun Filemonrayku 
\p  
\v 23 Wawkinchi Epafraspas Kristu Jesuspa shiminta yachachishkanrayku karselpi churay tukushka masini kanrayku saluduta kachahun.  
\v 24 Chaymanta Yaya Diospa shiminta yachachik masinikuna Markus, Aristarko, Demas, Lukaspas kanraykumi saluduta kachahunkuna. 
\p  
\v 25 Amunchi Jesukristu kankunata llakichishpan munashkanta karan shuk kankunapi paktachichun. \sig Chayllata killkashkanchi.\sig*\sig Wawkikichi Pablo, Timoteo\sig*